# CRM-GTD Smart Git Flow Configuration
# This file documents our branching strategy

## Branch Structure:
# master          - Main branch (latest stable)
# production-v1   - Current production version (V1 stable)
# develop-v1      - V1 development (bug fixes, minor improvements)
# develop-v2      - V2 development (new features, major changes)
# feature/*       - Feature branches
# hotfix/*        - Critical production fixes

## Workflow:
# 1. V1 Production: production-v1 branch
# 2. V1 Development: develop-v1 branch 
# 3. V2 Development: develop-v2 branch
# 4. Hotfixes: hotfix/* -> production-v1 -> develop-v1
# 5. V1 Features: feature/v1-* -> develop-v1
# 6. V2 Features: feature/v2-* -> develop-v2

## Version URLs:
# V1 Production: http://91.99.50.80/crm/
# V2 Development: http://91.99.50.80/crm2/

## Environment Variables:
# V1: .env.v1, docker-compose.v1.yml
# V2: .env.v2, docker-compose.v2.yml